        <amcr:nazev>Davle - Cult Area 1 - St. John the Baptist Monastery on the Island</amcr:nazev>
        <amcr:popis>The Benedictine Monastery of St John the Baptist was established around 1000 as the oldest male monastery in our territory. It was severely damaged at the time of the Brandenburg looting following the death of Přemysl Otakar II. (1278) and finally died after the Hussite Wars.</amcr:popis>
        <amcr:poznamka>Navigation point: N 49°52'50.18", E 14°23'26.70" (northern edge of the monastery compound on the island).</amcr:poznamka>
      </amcr:chranene_udaje>
